{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/python/python-program-idle/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Entering commands at the prompt is just the beginning. Let’s use IDLE to save and run files. With this skill you’ll be able to write and build complex and powerful Python programs. IDLE has two modes: interactive and script. We wrote our first program, “Hello, World!” in interactive mode. Interactive mode immediately returns the results of commands you enter into the shell. In script mode, you will write a script and then run it.</p>\n<p>Let’s create a module. We’ll cover modules in depth later. For now, all you need to know is that a module is a file containing Python code ending in the suffix:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.py</code></pre></div>\n<p>If it’s not already running, start IDLE. Using IDLE is very similar to using a text editor. Under File, select New Window or press <strong>Ctrl + N</strong>. That will bring up a new window titled, “Untitled”.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 528px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'223\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20223\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M104%2044l-3%208-3%206c-3%206-2%2018%203%2025l2%203v69c0%2067%200%2068%202%2068s2-1%202-67c0-63%200-67%202-67%206%202%2011%203%2017%201l7-1%202-1v-1h2v-2h2v-3c1-2%205-2%20131-2a3208%203208%200%20001-2H141l1-4%202-4c2%202%204%200%204-4v-4l-2%202-2%202-2-5c-4-14-21-21-33-15l-3%202v-4l-1-4-1%204m222%200l-3%201-4%201c-1%202-2%202-2%200l-6-2h-4v3c0%203%200%204%202%204l1-1%203-3c2-1%202-1%203%202v5l3-4c2-4%203-4%203-1%200%202%201%202%203%202s3%200%203-2l1-2%201%202%201%202c2%200%201-5-1-6l-2-1-1-1-1%201m-211%206l-6%203-3%202v23h29l1-3c2-3%201-14-1-17-4-6-14-10-20-8m94%2014c0%202-1%202-1%201h-3c-1%201-2%201-2-1l-3-1c-3%200-3%200-3%205l-1%204h4c3%200%204%200%203-1v-2h1c1%202%209%202%2010%200h2c2%202%204%201%204-2s-2-3-2%200l-1%203v-3c0-2-2-3-2-1h-1l-1-1-2-2c-1-1-1-1-2%201m136%200c0%202%200%202-1%201h-5l-1-2-1%202-1%201-1-1c0-4-2-2-2%203-1%204-1%204%203%204%202%200%203%200%203-2h5l-2-1v-1c2%200%205%202%205%204%200%201%201%201%203-1%203-2%203-6%200-6l-4-2c-1-1-1-1-1%201M107%2081s1%202%203%202l2%201c0-2%204-1%204%201%201%202%205%203%205%201l2-1h1l2-1c1%201%203%200%205-2l3-2h-14l-13%201\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IDLE\"\n        title=\"IDLE\"\n        src=\"/static/c322ab5212328f4d27a6fd0bf24dd7f0/0c3b4/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c322ab5212328f4d27a6fd0bf24dd7f0/58794/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle01.png 240w,\n/static/c322ab5212328f4d27a6fd0bf24dd7f0/3166f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle01.png 480w,\n/static/c322ab5212328f4d27a6fd0bf24dd7f0/0c3b4/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle01.png 528w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 528px) 100vw, 528px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Enter this command in the Untitled window:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>“What's brown <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> sounds like a bell?”<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>We need to save our file before we can run it. So under File, select Save. At the prompt, name it something clever like:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">badjoke.py</code></pre></div>\n<p>And save it somewhere you can find it later.</p>\n<p>Now the fun part. Under Run, select Run Module.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 669px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.41666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'222\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20222\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M399%201l-1%2016v14H252l-145-1c0-2%206-6%206-5h10l1-2h1c0%202%202%203%205%202v-2c0-3-1-3-2-2h-2l-5-1h-3l-2-1-3%201-2%201c-2%200-3-2-5-6-2-6-3-9-1-6l2%201-1-2V7l1-1-1-1h-6l-5-1H81c-5%202-13%202-15%200H52c-3%200-3%200-3%203%200%204%200%204%203%201%202-2%202-2%203%200v3c-1%203%202%201%204-2%201-3%201-3%201-1%200%203%206%203%206%200h1l1%202c4-1%204%200%202%203l-2%205c0%202-3%204-3%203H52l-2%201v-1c2%200%201-2-1-2s-2%201-2%203l1%203%201-1%201-1%201%202c0%203%205%202%206%200%200-3%202-4%202-1h1l1-1c0%203%202%203%202%200h1l2%202%202%203%201%203H0v96a1741%201741%200%20002%201V33h68l3%203c7%208%2025%208%2031-1l1-2h286v190l1-92V39h7l-1%2092%201%2091a6469%206469%200%20000-221M137%205c0%202%200%202-2%201-2-2-5%200-4%202s5%203%205%201h1l6%201%207%201h2l2-1%202-2h1v4l3-3c1-3%200-5-1-3h-4l-2-1c-2%200-3%201-3%202%200%202-2%202-3%200-1-3-4-2-5%200l-1%201V7l-2-3c-2-1-2-1-2%201m36-1l-2%204c0%204%201%203%202%200%201-2%201-2%201%200s2%203%202%200h1c0%202%2010%202%2010%200h1c0%203%202%203%202%200h1l2%202h4c2%201%203%201%204-2l1-3v3c-1%204%201%205%202%203%200-1%201-2%203-1%202%200%202%200%202-2%200-3-4-4-4-1-1%201-1%200-1-1l-1-3c-1%200-4%203-4%205l-1-1c-1-2-13-3-13-1h-1l-4-1-4-1h-3m105%202v4h7l7%201%201%201%201-1%202-1%201-2c0-2%200-3-2-3l-3%201h-1l-6-1-5-1-1-1-1%203m-19%200h-12l-1%201-1-2c-2%200-3%202-2%203v1l4%201%205-1h1c0%202%202%201%202-1l1%201c1%203%203%203%204-1%201-3%201-3%201-1%200%203%200%203%206%203l5-1%202-1v1c-1%201-1%201%201%201l2-2c0-2-1-3-2-3l-2%201h-1l-3-1h-3c-1-2-7-1-7%201M90%209l-5%201c-9-1-16%2010-11%2019%201%202%202%202%2014%202%2015%200%2015%200%2015-8%200-4-2-9-4-11l-9-3m48%2014c0%204%201%204%203%204%203%200%208-2%208-4h1c0%202%204%203%206%202h9l1-1%201-1v2h3v-3l-6-1h-8c0-2-1-2-3%200h-3l-2-1h-1l-3-1-3%201h-1c-2-1-2-1-2%203M0%20127\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Running a Python program in IDLE\"\n        title=\"Running a Python program in IDLE\"\n        src=\"/static/3d3101d3e4a6248fbd8698119e94b1da/4a11f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3d3101d3e4a6248fbd8698119e94b1da/58794/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle03.png 240w,\n/static/3d3101d3e4a6248fbd8698119e94b1da/3166f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle03.png 480w,\n/static/3d3101d3e4a6248fbd8698119e94b1da/4a11f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle03.png 669w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 669px) 100vw, 669px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now go back to the Shell. What’s this RESTART business? The Shell is restarted every time you run a module in IDLE. That’s to clear out any old settings that might interfere with your program. Below the RESTART line you should see:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 669px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.41666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'222\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20222\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M0%20111a2345%202345%200%20002%2017V33h389v189h10V0h-2l-2%201H2v3C1%206%201%206%201%203V0L0%20111m0%201a8531%208531%200%20001%202l1-99h198a6978%206978%200%2000-116-2H1V7L0%20112\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Running a Python program in IDLE\"\n        title=\"Running a Python program in IDLE\"\n        src=\"/static/b7e62540c0f0750b45989b93278131ad/4a11f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b7e62540c0f0750b45989b93278131ad/58794/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle04.png 240w,\n/static/b7e62540c0f0750b45989b93278131ad/3166f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle04.png 480w,\n/static/b7e62540c0f0750b45989b93278131ad/4a11f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle04.png 669w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 669px) 100vw, 669px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>It’s not much of a joke without a punchline. Let’s modify our module. Change the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token builtin\">input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>“What's brown <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> sound like a bell?”<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>“Dung!”<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Let’s run that again, this time with the keyboard shortcut: <strong>F5</strong>. Try that.</p>\n<p>In the Shell you’ll see our joke printed, but where’s the punchline? Notice that there isn’t a prompt? That’s because the Shell is waiting for your input. Press any key.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 669px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.41666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'222\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20222\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M399%201l-1%2016v14H0v96a1741%201741%200%20002%201V33h389v190l1-93a2725%202725%200%20014-96c2%202%201%204-1%204-2%201-2%201%201%201h3l-1%2092%201%2091c1-1%202-23%202-108a570%20570%200%2000-2-113M174%204l-3%201-3%201h-1l-4-2c-4%200-4%200-4%203%200%202%200%203%202%203l1-1%201-1c3-1%204%201%203%203v1l3-3c1-3%201-3%202-1%200%203%205%203%205%200h1c0%202%2010%202%2010%200h1l1%202%201-2c-1-3-4-4-5-2h-1l-2-1-2%201h-1l-1-1-2-1-1-1-1%201M73%2020l-1%204c0%203%201%203%203%203l3-1%203-1h9c2-1%202-1%202%201s3%201%204-2c0-3-2-5-3-3h-3l-1%202-1-1-1-1-2-1H73m32%200l-1%204c0%203%201%203%204%203l3-1%206-1c7%200%208%200%208-2h1c0%202%203%203%205%202v-3c0-2-1-3-3-1h-1l-5-1h-3l-2-1-3%201h-9m34%203c0%204%201%204%204%204l4-1%201-1%202-2h1c0%202%205%203%206%202h8l2-1%201-1%201%201v1c2%200%203%200%203-2-1-2-1-2-7-2l-7-1h-3l-3%201-2-1h-2l-1-1-2%201h-4l-1-1-1%204M0%20127\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Running a Python program in IDLE\"\n        title=\"Running a Python program in IDLE\"\n        src=\"/static/becd5714739bd8974f1bc56fadcd2bd4/4a11f/20140531_python_bytes01.03idle05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/becd5714739bd8974f